Configure registration form and event page layout
If you don’t need to request additional details to ticket buyers other than First name, Last name, and Email, you can skip this step: after purchasing, a confirmation email will be directly sent to the ticket holder with the ticket attached in pdf format.

If you need to request additional information, configure the registration form by adding all required fields: the ticket holder will receive an email with a request to complete registration, with a link to this page. After completing his registration, the ticket holder will receive a confirmation email with his ticket attached in pdf format.
